# Since configuration is handled natively via MT5 Indicator Inputs (which writes config.json),
# environment variables aren't strictly required for core functionality.
# However, if you plan to add the AI/LLM components mentioned in the architecture docs,
# you can define your API keys here.

# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-...
# LOCAL_LLM_URL=http://localhost:11434
